pfind performs relational pathfinding

PARAMS
ldbFile    = file containing motif (output of getcom), e.g., myMotifs.comb.ldb
maxLen     = max length of clause to be found
maxFreeVar = max number of variables that appear only once in a clause
maxVar     = max number of variables in a clause
hrLimit    = time limit on running pfind (in hours). Negative value means no limit
declFile   = file specifying predicate declaration (same as rwl)
outFile    = output file containing rules, e.g., myRules.rules
